      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROCKNROLL ROCKET (3) had been building to a win and achieved it at this circuit and distance last week, leading from this barrier and going on to score by 1.6 metres. Stays at a similar level and should push forward again so can go back to back. ALWAYS PROMISE ME (2) has come from wider barriers in his last two outings and put together a string of runner-up results here prior. Enjoys a far better starting position so can play a major role. ADDOCAR (1) will strip fitter so is in the mix having come from this barrier for a respectable third when resuming at this circuit and distance last week. PEPPI GRATZ (4) draws lower than last week and can feature if he can recapture the form from two starts back that saw him score over this distance at Tamworth.",
